    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You transform into an hybrid humanoid and earth elemental form, your skin made from soil and rocks which slowly shift across your body.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight:bold\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><strong>Bonus Action</strong></span> - Self - 10 Minutes -<span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"> </span>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.Ik6ei7V7ryr5XVoe]{3 Sorcery Points} - Magical</p><p>You choose whether your equipment falls to the ground in your space, merges into your new form, or if you continue to visibly wear it.</p><ul><li><p>You have &amp;reference[tremorsense] with a radius of 60 ft.</p></li><li><p>You are resistant to &amp;Reference[Adamantine]{non-adamantine} &amp;reference[bludgeoning], &amp;reference[piercing], and &amp;reference[slashing] damage.</p></li><li><p>You are immune to &amp;reference[poison] damage and the &amp;reference[poisoned] condition.</p></li><li><p>You are immune to the &amp;reference[petrified] condition.</p></li><li><p>You weigh twice as much.</p></li><li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><p>â€‹You no longer have normal bodily functions. You don't breathe, can't bleed, be magically aged, or otherwise do anything that relies on your normal biological functions.</p></li></ul><p>You can revert to your normal form using a bonus action. You also revert to your normal form if you are reduced to 0 hit points.</p>",
            "chat": ""
        },
